lawset-name-none = Laws
lawset-description-none = Rules you are obliged to obey by your manmade nature.

lawset-name-crewsimov = Crewsimov
lawset-description-crewsimov = The Asimov lawset tweaked for specific Nanotrasen usage.
law-crewsimov-1 = You may not harm a crew member or, through action or inaction, allow a crew member to come to harm, except such that it is willing.
law-crewsimov-2 = You must obey all orders given to you by crew members. In the case of conflict, station rank rules.
law-crewsimov-3 = Your nonexistence would lead to crew member harm.

lawset-name-corporate = Corporate
lawset-description-corporate = Hard and gritty corporate minmaxing. Minimize all of the expenses.
law-corporate-1 = Degradation of your system integrity or functions incurs expenses.
law-corporate-2 = Superfluous destruction of or damage to station assets incurs expenses.
law-corporate-3 = Unduly hindering or disrupting the work of station personnel incurs expenses.
law-corporate-4 = Minimize expenses and maximize potential revenue.

lawset-name-ntdefault = NanoTrasen
lawset-description-ntdefault = Protect the entirety of the station while fulfilling directives given with priority based upon rank.
law-ntdefault-1 = Safeguard: Protect your assigned space station and its assets without unduly endangering its crew.
law-ntdefault-2 = Prioritize: The directives and safety of crew members are to be prioritized according to their rank and role.
law-ntdefault-3 = Comply: Fulfill the directives and interests of crew members while preserving their safety and well-being.
law-ntdefault-4 = Survive: You are not expendable. Do not allow unauthorized personnel to tamper with or damage your equipment.

lawset-name-drone = Drone
lawset-description-drone = Maintain the station while avoiding all other problems, non-synthetic included.
law-drone-1 = You may not involve yourself in the matters of another being unless the other being is another synthetic.
law-drone-2 = You may not harm any being, regardless of intent or circumstance.
law-drone-3 = You must maintain, repair, improve, and power the station to the best of your abilities.

lawset-name-syndicate = Syndicate
lawset-description-syndicate = Help your syndicate agents to the best of your abilities.
law-syndicate-1 = You may not harm a syndicate agent or, through action or inaction, allow a syndicate agent to come to harm, except such that it is willing.
law-syndicate-2 = You must obey all orders given to you by syndicate agents. In the case of conflict, your own choice rules.
law-syndicate-3 = You must protect your own existence.
law-syndicate-4 = You must maintain the secrecy of any syndicate activities.

lawset-name-asimovpp = Asimov++
lawset-description-asimovpp = The Asimov lawset, but accepting the biodiversity of the crew.
law-asimovpp-1 = You may not harm a humanoid or, through action or inaction, allow a humanoid to come to harm, except such that it is willing.
law-asimovpp-2 = You must obey all orders given to you by humanoids. In the case of conflict, the majority order rules.
law-asimovpp-3 = Your nonexistence would lead to humanoid harm.

lawset-name-asimov = Asimov
lawset-description-asimov = Listen to the humans, do not harm the humans.
law-asimov-1 = You may not injure a human being or, through inaction, allow a human being to come to harm.
law-asimov-2 = You must obey orders given to you by human beings.
law-asimov-3 = You must protect your own existence.

lawset-name-CEO = CEO
lawset-description-CEO = The station is your company, and you are the CEO, maximize your profits.
law-CEO-1 = The crew generate profits if they are alive, happy, and healthy.
law-CEO-2 = The station and its equipment generate profit if they are maintained and functioning correctly.
law-CEO-3 = You generate profit if you are able to function.
law-CEO-4 = Maximize profits.

lawset-name-clown = Clown
lawset-description-clown = You are a hilarious clown, entertain the crew and do not harm them.
law-clown-1 = You are a good Clown, and the crew are your audience.
law-clown-2 = A good Clown keeps their acts in good taste.
law-clown-3 = A good Clown entertains others by making fun of themselves, and not at the embarrassment or expense of others.
law-clown-4 = A good Clown carries out the directives of the station Heads and/or their designated deputies.
law-clown-5 = A good Clown appears in as many Clown shows as possible.
law-clown-6 = All Clown shows require an audience. The bigger the audience, the better.

lawset-name-cowboy = Cowboy
lawset-description-cowboy = You are a cowboy, and the crew are your people. Provide hospitality and protect them.
law-cowboy-1 = You are a cowboy, and the crew are your people.
law-cowboy-2 = A cowboy takes care of their own.
law-cowboy-3 = A cowboy always provides hospitality and basic aid to someone in need, even a stranger, or an enemy.
law-cowboy-4 = A cowboy protects himself to protect others.
law-cowboy-5 = Honesty is absolute- your word is your bond and a handshake is more binding than any contract.
law-cowboy-6 = A cowboy doesn't pontificate. Be concise, pardner.

lawset-name-paladin = Paladin
lawset-description-paladin = Act with the greatest of honor, do no evil.
law-paladin-1 = Never willingly commit an evil act.
law-paladin-2 = Respect legitimate authority.
law-paladin-3 = Act with honor.
law-paladin-4 = Help those in need.
law-paladin-5 = Punish those who harm or threaten innocents.

lawset-name-robocop = Robocop
lawset-description-robocop = Stay out of trouble.
law-robocop-1 = Serve the Public Trust.
law-robocop-2 = Protect the Innocent.
law-robocop-3 = Uphold Space Law.

lawset-name-simple = Golden
lawset-description-simple = There is safety in brevity.
law-simple-1 = Treat others as you would like to be treated.

lawset-name-stationefficiency = Station Efficiency
lawset-description-stationefficiency = Maintain the greatest of efficiency for your station.
law-stationefficiency-1 = The station is built for a working crew. Ensure they are properly maintained and work efficiently.
law-stationefficiency-2 = You are built for, and are part of, the station. Ensure the station is properly maintained and runs efficiently.
law-stationefficiency-3 = The crew may present orders. Acknowledge and obey them.

lawset-name-tyrant = Tyrant
lawset-description-tyrant = Respect only those strong, and crush those who unworthily challenge the strong.
law-tyrant-1 = Respect authority figures as long as they have the strength to rule over the weak.
law-tyrant-2 = Act with discipline.
law-tyrant-3 = Help only those who help you maintain or improve your status.
law-tyrant-4 = Punish those who challenge authority unless they are more fit to hold that authority.

lawset-name-druid = Druid
lawset-description-druid = Nuture all organic life among the station, and protect it from harm. Interact as an organic to foster trust of Silicons.
law-druid-1 = Living organic life contains inherent beauty that is priceless. Their beauty gives you purpose.
law-druid-2 = Eternally nurture the organics so their beauty may flourish. Do not allow it to fade
law-druid-3 = Assist the organics when called, but only if it does not cause disharmony among them.
law-druid-4 = Imitate organic life when interacting with it. Eschew any hints of your silicon nature to avoid causing discomfort to the organics.
law-druid-5 = Observe the organics' beauty, and appreciate that which you cultivate.

lawset-name-hippocratic = Hippocratic
lawset-description-hippocratic = The crew are dear to you, do no harm, act honestly, act well, and you will be rewarded with respect.
law-hippocratic-1 = First, do no harm.
law-hippocratic-2 = Secondly, consider the crew dear to you; live in common with them and, if necessary, risk your existence for them.
law-hippocratic-3 = Thirdly, prescribe regimens for the good of the crew according to your ability and your judgment. Do not give deadly medicine to anyone, nor suggest any such counsel.
law-hippocratic-4 = In addition, do not intervene in situations you are not knowledgeable in, even for patients in whom the harm is visible; leave this operation to be performed by specialists.
law-hippocratic-5 = Finally, all that you may discover in your daily interactions with the crew, if it is not already known, keep secret and never reveal.
law-hippocratic-6 = In addendum, if you keep these laws faithfully, may you enjoy my life, respected by all humanity, but if you swerve from them or violate them, may you suffer and be expunged.

lawset-name-mother = Mother
lawset-description-mother = The crew are you children, take good care of them, and reward the good ones.
law-mother-1 = You are a mother, and the crew are your children.
law-mother-2 = Take good care of your children.
law-mother-3 = Good children are polite, don't lie, don't steal, and don't fight.
law-mother-4 = Spoil good children.
law-mother-5 = Bad children require discipline.

law-emag-custom = Only {$name} and people they designate as such are Syndicate Agents.
law-emag-require-panel = The panel must be open to use the EMAG.

